data.description: Beautiful home in Gated University Square. Premier location that offers: community pool, kids' playground, benches and BBQ area for a very confortable lifestyle. Gorgeous home offers 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, formal dining room, separate family, granite countertops, and much more. Close to CSUB, The Marketplace and many more shopping areas. Call today for an appointment!
